<title>USA: Safeguard Sci proposes MicroVision offer.</title>
<headline>Safeguard Sci proposes MicroVision offer.</headline>
<dateline>WAYNE, Pa. 1997-04-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Safegurad Scientifics Inc said Tuesday its MicroVision Medical Systems Inc is proposing to distribute to Safeguard's shareholders rights to purchase common shares, subject to the filing of a registration statement with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission.</p>
<p>MicroVision plans to change its name to ChromaVision Medical Systems Inc.</p>
<p>Safeguard recently offered rights to its Diamond Technology Partners and Sanchez Computer Associates units.</p>
